trans-unit.source: Exposes <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> types to UI Automation.
trans-unit.target: Expone los tipos <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> a la automatización de la interfaz de usuario.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Creates a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> for the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" />.
trans-unit.target: Crea un <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> para el <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> for the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> para el <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: This <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer> remains in memory until the associated <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement> is destroyed.
trans-unit.target: Esto <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer> permanece en memoria hasta que el asociado <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement> se destruye.

trans-unit.source: The same instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer> is returned from subsequent calls to this method and to calls to <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer.FromElement%2A>.
trans-unit.target: La misma instancia de la <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer> se devuelve desde las llamadas subsiguientes a este método y en las llamadas a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer.FromElement%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The type of the peer is determined by the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.OnCreateAutomationPeer%2A> virtual callback.
trans-unit.target: El tipo del mismo nivel viene determinado por la <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.OnCreateAutomationPeer%2A> devolución de llamada virtual.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkContentElement> does not implement the callback, no <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer> is created and this method returns `null`.
trans-unit.target: Si <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkContentElement> no implementa la devolución de llamada, ya no <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer> se crea y devuelve este método `null`.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> for the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> para el <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> for the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" />, or <see langword="null" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> has not been created by the <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer.CreatePeerForElement(System.Windows.ContentElement)" /> method.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> para el <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> especificado o <see langword="null" /> si el método <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> aún no ha creado <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer.CreatePeerForElement(System.Windows.ContentElement)" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the accelerator key for the element associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la tecla de método abreviado del elemento asociado a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAcceleratorKey" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAcceleratorKey" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="F:System.String.Empty" /> string.
trans-unit.target: Cadena <see cref="F:System.String.Empty" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the access key for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la tecla de acceso del elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAccessKey" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAccessKey" />.

trans-unit.source: The access key for this <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" />.
trans-unit.target: Tecla de acceso de <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the control type for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el tipo de control correspondiente al control <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlType" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlType" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationControlType.Custom" /> enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: El valor de enumeración <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationControlType.Custom" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the string that uniquely identifies the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la cadena que identifica de manera única el elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a esta clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAutomationId" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAutomationId" />.

trans-unit.source: A string containing the automation identifier.
trans-unit.target: Una cadena que contiene el identificador de automatización.

trans-unit.source: The value of the automation identifier is the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperties.AutomationId%2A> property, and if that isn't set, it's the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Name%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: El valor del identificador de automatización es el <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperties.AutomationId%2A> propiedad, y si es que no está configurado, es el <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Name%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" /> representing the bounding rectangle of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el <see cref="T:System.Windows.Rect" /> que representa el rectángulo delimitador del <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetBoundingRectangle" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetBoundingRectangle" />.

trans-unit.source: The bounding rectangle.
trans-unit.target: Rectángulo delimitador.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of child elements of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la colección de elementos secundarios del control <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetChildren" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetChildren" />.

trans-unit.source: The collection of child elements.
trans-unit.target: Colección de elementos secundarios.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el nombre del control <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a esta clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClassName" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClassName" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="F:System.String.Empty" /> string.
trans-unit.target: Cadena <see cref="F:System.String.Empty" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Point" /> that represents the clickable space that is on the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un <see cref="T:System.Windows.Point" /> que representa el espacio interactivo que se encuentra en <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> que está asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClickablePoint" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClickablePoint" />.

trans-unit.source: The point that represents the clickable space that is on the element.
trans-unit.target: El punto que representa el espacio interactivo que se encuentra en el elemento.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the element is a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>, the clickable point is any point that is within the visible client area of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button> that would result in issuing the command that the button represents, when the user clicks the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button> by using the mouse.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, si el elemento es un <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>, el punto donde hacer clic es cualquier punto dentro del área de cliente visible de la <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button> que daría como resultado de emitir el comando que representa el botón, cuando el usuario hace clic en el <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button> mediante el mouse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the string that describes the functionality of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la cadena que describe la funcionalidad del <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetHelpText" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetHelpText" />.

trans-unit.source: The string that describes the functionality of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Cadena que describe la funcionalidad del elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: The string that is returned generally is the same text that is provided in the tooltip for the control.
trans-unit.target: La cadena que se devuelve por lo general es el mismo texto que se proporciona en la información sobre herramientas para el control.

trans-unit.source: Gets a string that conveys the visual status of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene una cadena que transmite el estado visual del <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetItemStatus" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetItemStatus" />.

trans-unit.source: A string containing the status.
trans-unit.target: Cadena que contiene el estado.

trans-unit.source: For example, the status of a messenger contact could be "Busy" or "Online".
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, el estado de un contacto de messenger podría ser "Ocupado" o "En línea".

trans-unit.source: Gets a human-readable string that contains the type of the item that the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene una cadena legible que contiene el tipo del elemento al que representa el <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetItemType" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetItemType" />.

trans-unit.source: The string that contains the item type.
trans-unit.target: Cadena que contiene el tipo de elemento.

trans-unit.source: Examples are "Mail Message", "Contact", and "Document".
trans-unit.target: Algunos ejemplos son "Mensaje de correo", "Contacto" y "Documento".

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer" /> for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Label" /> that is targeted to the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer" /> para <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Label" /> que tiene como destino <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado con <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetLabeledBy" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetLabeledBy" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.LabelAutomationPeer" /> for the element that is targeted by the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Label" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.LabelAutomationPeer" /> para el elemento que <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Label" /> tiene como destino.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the element is a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox> control, the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetLabeledBy%2A> method could get the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer> for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Label> that is associated with the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox>.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, si el elemento es un <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox> (control), el <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetLabeledBy%2A> método podría obtener el <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer> para el <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Label> que está asociada con el <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the notification characteristics of the live region of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene las características de notificación de la región activa del elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> que está asociado a este elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetLiveSetting" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetLiveSetting" />.

trans-unit.source: The notification characteristics of the live region.
trans-unit.target: Características de notificación de la región activa.

trans-unit.source: Gets the text label of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la etiqueta de texto del <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetName" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetName" />.

trans-unit.source: The string that contains the label.
trans-unit.target: Cadena que contiene la etiqueta.

trans-unit.source: The name property can be thought of as the string of text that a user would use to explain which control is being referred to.
trans-unit.target: La propiedad name puede considerarse como una cadena de texto que un usuario debe usar para explicar qué control se hace referencia.

trans-unit.source: It is important to have a textual representation for all controls in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_gui](~/includes/tlasharptla-gui-md.md)] so that you can programmatically refer to the control in a localized manner.
trans-unit.target: Es importante tener una representación textual de todos los controles en el [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_gui](~/includes/tlasharptla-gui-md.md)] por lo que puede hacer referencia al control mediante programación en su forma adaptada.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> is laid out in a specific direction.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor que indica si el <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> está colocado en una dirección determinada.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetOrientation" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetOrientation" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationOrientation.None" /> enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: El valor de enumeración <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationOrientation.None" />.

trans-unit.source: One of the enumeration values.
trans-unit.target: Uno de los valores de enumeración.

trans-unit.source: Gets the control pattern for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el patrón de control para <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: An object that implements the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISynchronizedInputProvider" /> interface if <paramref name="patternInterface" /> is <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SynchronizedInput" />; otherwise, <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Objeto que implementa la interfaz <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISynchronizedInputProvider" /> si <paramref name="patternInterface" /> es <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SynchronizedInput" />; de lo contrario, es <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> currently has keyboard input focus.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor que indica si <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> que se asocia a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> tiene actualmente enfoque de entrada de teclado.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.HasKeyboardFocus" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.HasKeyboardFocus" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the element has keyboard input focus; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> si el elemento tiene enfoque de entrada de teclado; en caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> is an element that contains data that is presented to the user.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor que indica si el objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> que está asociado a este objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> es un elemento que contiene datos que se presentan al usuario.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.IsContentElement" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.IsContentElement" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> is something that the end user would understand as being interactive or as contributing to the logical structure of the control in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_gui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-gui-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor que indica si el usuario final entiende como interactivo el <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> o entiende que contribuye a la estructura lógica del control en [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_gui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-gui-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.IsControlElement" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.IsControlElement" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether this automation peer can receive and send events to the associated element.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor que indica si esta automatización del mismo nivel puede recibir y enviar eventos al elemento asociado.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.IsEnabled" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.IsEnabled" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the automation peer can receive and send events; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> si la automatización del mismo nivel puede recibir y enviar eventos; de lo contrario, es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> can accept keyboard focus.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor que indica si el <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> puede aceptar el foco de teclado.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.IsKeyboardFocusable" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.IsKeyboardFocusable" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> is off of the screen.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor que indica si el <see cref="T:System.Windows.ContentElement" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer" /> está fuera de la pantalla.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.IsOffscreen" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.IsOffscreen" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the element is not on the screen; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> si el elemento no está en la pantalla; de lo contrario, es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: This property does not indicate whether the element is visible.
trans-unit.target: Esta propiedad no indica si el elemento está visible.

trans-unit.source: In some circumstances, an element can be on the screen but still not be visible, for example if the element is obscured by other elements.
trans-unit.target: En algunas circunstancias, un elemento puede estar en la pantalla pero no estarán visibles, por ejemplo, si el elemento está oculto por otros elementos.

trans-unit.source: In this case the method would return `false`.
trans-unit.target: En este caso, el método devolverá `false`.
